OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies faces vote on the
OL,4,Cfuture of his leadership
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservative leader will
OL,7,Fface a vote on the future of his
OL,8,Fleadership next week.
OL,10,FAndrew RT Davies has called for the
OL,11,Fvote to be held by Senedd
OL,12,FConservatives in their regular group
OL,13,Fmeeting next Tuesday.
OL,15,FIt follows a meeting he held today
OL,16,Fwith a group of fellow MSs who, I
OL,17,Funderstand, expressed dissatisfaction
OL,18,Fwith Mr Davies' leadership.
