OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies faces vote on the
OL,4,Cfuture of his leadership
OL,6,FI'm told that those he met today do
OL,7,Fnot represent a majority of the Senedd
OL,8,Fgroup.
OL,10,FIn response to their concerns, Andrew
OL,11,FRT Davies has asked for a motion of
OL,12,Fconfidence to be discussed in the
OL,13,Fmeeting on Tuesday and a recorded vote
OL,14,Ftaken.
OL,16,FThere have been rumblings about Mr
OL,17,FDavies' leadership in recent months,
OL,18,Fwith some concerns spilling out in
OL,19,Fpublic.
