OL,6,FSome came after he posted a photo on
OL,7,Fsocial media from the Vale of
OL,8,FGlamorgan County Show earlier this
OL,9,Fyear inviting people to have their say
OL,10,Fon abolishing the Senedd.
OL,12,FFellow Shadow Cabinet members made
OL,13,Fpublic statements saying that the
OL,14,Fparty doesn't support abolition and
OL,15,Ffollowing that Mr Davies told the
OL,16,FSharp End programme that "It isn't
OL,17,FConservative policy" and that "our
OL,18,Fpolicy is to make devolution work for
OL,19,Fthe people of Wales."
