OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies faces vote on the
OL,4,Cfuture of his leadership
OL,6,FMore recently he received an official
OL,7,Freprimand in October after the
OL,8,FSenedd's Standards Committee endorsed
OL,9,Fa finding by the Standards
OL,10,FCommissioner that he brought the Welsh
OL,11,FParliament into disrepute by calling
OL,12,FWales' 20mph speed limit a "blanket"
OL,13,Fpolicy on social media.
