OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies faces vote on the
OL,4,Cfuture of his leadership
OL,6,FThe Commissioner Douglas Bain said
OL,7,Fthat as "Leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives and a former experienced
OL,9,Fmember of the Standards of Conduct
OL,10,FCommittee it was incumbent of the
OL,11,FMember to set a good example and to
OL,12,Ffollow the guidance given by the
OL,13,FCommittee and in the Guidance on the
OL,14,FCode of Conduct."
OL,16,FIn response to the reprimand, Mr
OL,17,FDavies said that his choice of words
OL,18,Fwas "a matter of opinion."
