OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies faces vote on the
OL,4,Cfuture of his leadership
OL,6,FA farmer and campaigner on rural
OL,7,Fissues, Andrew RT Davies became a
OL,8,FConservative Assembly member in 2007.
OL,10,FHe was elected leader in 2011 but was
OL,11,Fforced to quit after losing the
OL,12,Fsupport of his group in 2018. Three
OL,13,Fyears later, he returned to the top
OL,14,Fjob and has been in charge ever since.
